dden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 29, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cew1665702621348.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cew1665702621348.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cew1665702621348.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cew1665702621348\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Test if a constant has been defined.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cew1665702621348__topic_d93293e1_d93294e1_d93295e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93296e1_d93297e1_d93298e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#ifdefined</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Constant</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93299e1_d93300e1_d93301e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt; Precompiler directives and ProcScript statements &gt;</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93302e1_d93303e1_d93304e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#endif</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cew1665702621348__section_v52_1sc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747142e78\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93530e1_d93531e1_d93532e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Constant</var>—constant name</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cew1665702621348__section_epd_2sc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747142e90\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93314e1_d93315e1_d93316e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#ifdefined</span> directive can be\n            used to create a block of ProcScript statements and precompiler directives whenever the\n            constant specified already exists.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cew1665702621348__section_kzt_fsc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747142e102\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93317e1_d93318e1_d93319e1\">The following example adds a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">debug</span>\n            statement to the ProcScript being compiled if the constant\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 1:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cew1665702621348__pre_ukr_hsc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#ifdefined DEBUGGING\n #if (&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;=1)\n debug\n #endif\n#endif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cew1665702621348__ul_vkr_hsc_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cew1665702621348__li_d36461e1_d36462e1_d36463e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is not defined, no further code is generated. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cew1665702621348__li_d36464e1_d36465e1_d36466e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 0, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span>\n               directive is generated as follows: <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cew1665702621348__pre_ykr_hsc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#if (1=0)\n debug\n#endif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93320e1_d93321e1_d93322e1\">In this case, no ProcScript is generated.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cew1665702621348__li_d36467e1_d36468e1_d36469e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 1, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span>\n               directive is generated as follows: <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cew1665702621348__pre_alr_hsc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#if (1=1)\n debug\n#endif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cew1665702621348__p_d93323e1_d93324e1_d93325e1\">In this case, the following ProcScript statement\n                  is compiled:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cew1665702621348__pre_blr_hsc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">debug</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/syc1665702621424.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#ifundefined</a><p>Test if a constant has not been defined.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612333\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612333\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#ifdefined Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Test if a constant has been defined. #ifdefined Constant < Precompiler directives and ProcScript statements > #endif Parameters Constant —constant name Description The #ifdefined directive can be used to create a block of ProcScript statements and precompiler directives whenever the constant specified already exists. Example The following example adds a debug statement to the ProcScript being compiled if the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 1: #ifdefined DEBUGGING #if (<DEBUGGING>=1) debug #endif #endif Copy If the constant <DEBUGGING> is not defined, no further code is generated. If the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 0, the #if directive is generated as follows: #if (1=0) debug #endif Copy In this case, no ProcScript is generated. If the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 1, the #if directive is generated as follows: #if (1=1) debug #endif Copy In this case, the following ProcScript statement is compiled: debug Copy Related Links #ifundefined Test if a constant has not been defined. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}